title: [1508521049] Brussels Sprouts with Pancetta and Chestnuts - Gordon Ramsay
description:
From Christmas with Gordon (2010). Brussels Sprouts are blanched and sautéed with Italian bacon and chestnuts. These don't taste like any sprouts you've tasted before. 

Subscribe for weekly cooking videos.
